As the newcomer base explodes Ares and Sixshot fly out.
Ares: What the HELL was that?
Sixshot: Its seem Unitron was just a saboteur working for another person.... 
I suggest that we contact the other Predacons and see if we can't  join them 
and help them out.
Ares: Excellent idea.
They head off to Trypticon.

Rampage sits at his consol.
Rampage: Its been a while since we have heard from Brightblade.
Inferno: She may have been terminated.
Scourge: The base defenses will be on full every moment of every hour of 
every day.
Rampage: Lets hope no one else attacks.

OOC:(Yanshosh I need to ask you some questions later on.)
